scenes.description: Takanashi Kiara addresses her fans, thanking them for the year 2023 and introducing the final song of her birthday live.
Kiara performs the song 'Sleep Talking' from her album.
The audio becomes distorted due to technical issues as the next song begins; Kiara asks the staff to replay the start.
